@merlimat another user reported a similar issue of `java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Illegal base64 character 2d`.

This looks more like a convert issue between protobuf string (optional string partition_key   = 6) to bytes.

Maybe turn partition_key from protobuf `string` to `bytes`, could better solve this kind of issue. what do you think of this?

